# Ignore ALL generated analysis output under output/ (any comparison_id:
# output/<comparison_id>/rdata, figures, tables, ProtGridSearch.RData, etc.).
# Everything here is regenerated by knitting, so none of it needs committing.
# This file is self-contained (does not depend on the root .gitignore) and keeps
# the output/ folder present in the repo via the !.gitignore exception below.
*
!.gitignore
